user.description:
The MQTT broker configured in Home Assistant will be used:
 - Broker: {mqtt_broker}
 - Port:{mqtt_broker_port}
  - Authentication: {mqtt_user}

 This broker configuration will be added to each device with the name of this integration; 'ha-button-plus' and can be found in the Button+ interface.

 The buttons of the Button+ will be configured to send clicks on a topic in this broker and the integration will sync these with the home assistant button entities. 

 To continue, pick the desired option to setup your Button+ devices.
